# fyipedia — Unified CLI Demo
Output demo.gif

Set FontSize 14
Set Width 920
Set Height 620
Set Shell "zsh"
Set Theme "Catppuccin Mocha"
Set TypingSpeed 30ms
Set Padding 20

# Install + run CLI (uv creates temp env)
Type "uvx --from 'fyipedia[all]' fyi version"
Enter
Sleep 2.5s

# Color info
Type "uvx --from 'fyipedia[all]' fyi color info FF6B35"
Enter
Sleep 3s

# Unit conversion
Type "uvx --from 'fyipedia[all]' fyi unit convert 100 kilometer mile"
Enter
Sleep 3s

Sleep 1s
